                                    2019</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438402657160_001" name="s1" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><heading>Citation</heading><content>These regulations may be cited as the Land Registration Fees Regulations.</content></section><section id="ID_1438402657176_001" name="s1A" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="s1A"><num value="1A">1A.</num><heading>Interpretation</heading><leadIn>In these regulations, unless the context otherwise requires—</leadIn><def name="ComputerPrintout"><term>computer
                                printout</term>
                                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">電腦印製本</term>) has the meaning assigned
                        by <ref>regulation 2</ref> of the Land Registration Regulations (<ref href="/hk/cap128A">Cap. 128 sub. leg. A</ref>);
                        <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1986/ln248">L.N. 248 of
                                        1986</ref>)</sourceNote></def><def name="Instrument"><term>instrument</term>
                                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">文書</term>) includes any deed,
                        conveyance, lis pendens, judgment or other instrument in writing.
                        <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1992/56">56 of 1992 s.
                                        18</ref>; <ref href="hk/2019/er6">E.R. 6 of
                                2019</ref>)</sourceNote></def><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1981/ln139">L.N. 139 of 1981</ref>; <ref href="/hk/2002/20">20 of 2002 s. 5</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438402657191_001" name="s2" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><heading>Fees payable</heading><subsection id="ID_1438411154679_032" name="1" temporalId="s2_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content>The fees set forth in the <ref>Schedule</ref> shall be taken in the Land
                Registry for the matters therein mentioned.
                <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1996/ln35">L.N. 35 of
                    1996</ref>)</sourceNote></content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438411154679_040" name="2" temporalId="s2_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="/hk/1996/ln35">L.N. 35 of 1996</ref>)</sourceNote></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438411154679_048" name="3" temporalId="s2_3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content>A fee to be taken pursuant to this regulation in respect of any instrument
                delivered or redelivered for registration shall be paid by the person for whose
                benefit or on whose behalf the instrument is so delivered or redelivered.
                <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1981/ln139">L.N. 139 of
                    1981</ref>)</sourceNote></content><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1993/8">8 of 1993 s. 30</ref>)</sourceNote></subsection></section><section id="ID_1438402657207_001" name="s3" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="s3"><num value="3">3.</num><heading>Power to grant exemption</heading><content>The Land Registrar may waive any fee required to be taken in respect of any of the matters mentioned in the <ref>Schedule</ref> if he is satisfied that the fee would, if charged, be paid out of the general revenue.</content><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1980/56">56 of 1980 s. 12</ref>; <ref href="/hk/1993/8">8 of 1993 s. 30</ref>; <ref href="/hk/1996/ln35">L.N. 35 of 1996</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438402657207_003" name="s4" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2022-07-01" status="operational" temporalId="s4"><num value="4">4.</num><heading>Duty to grant exemption</heading><subsection id="ID_1438411154851_004" name="1" temporalId="s4_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><leadIn>Subject to paragraph (2), the Land Registrar shall waive the fee required to be
                taken under—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438411154851_012" name="a" temporalId="s4_1_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>item 10 of the <ref>Schedule</ref> for supplying a copy of any register
                    card; or
                    <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2002/20">20 of 2002 s.
                        5</ref>)</sourceNote></content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411154851_020" name="b" temporalId="s4_1_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>item 11 of the <ref>Schedule</ref> for supplying information,
                    <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2002/20">20 of 2002 s.
                        5</ref>)</sourceNote></content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411154851_028" name="c" temporalId="s4_1_c"><num value="c">(c)</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="/hk/2002/20">20 of 2002 s. 5</ref>)</sourceNote></paragraph><continued>if he is satisfied that the copy or information, as the case may be, is
                required in connection with a proposed incorporation of owners under the Building
                Management Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap344">Cap. 344</ref>).
                <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1996/ln35">L.N. 35 of
                    1996</ref>)</sourceNote></continued></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438411154851_041" name="2" temporalId="s4_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content>The fee required to be taken but waived under paragraph (1) shall be paid by
                the
                Secretary
                for Home and Youth Affairs out of the general revenue.
                <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1996/ln35">L.N. 35 of
                    1996</ref>; <ref href="hk/2022/ln144">L.N. 144 of 2022</ref>)</sourceNote></content></subsection><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1994/ln320">L.N. 320 of 1994</ref>)</sourceNote></section><schedule id="ID_1438402657222_002" name="sch0" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2025-07-16" status="operational" temporalId="sch0"><num value="0">Schedule</num><note class="align_right" role="crossReferences" type="inline">[<ref href="/hk/cap128B/s2">regs. 2</ref>, <ref href="/hk/cap128B/s3">3</ref> &amp; <ref href="/hk/cap128B/s4">4</ref>]</note><text>
